==Months of Yang Fire Tiger== The first month (January) of a year ending in 4 or 9 in the Western calendar (when the [[Heavenly Stems|stem]] is [[甲|Kō]] or [[己|Ki]]) is designated as a Heiin month. However, this is based on the [[Chinese lunar calendar|lunar calendar]] or the [[solar term calendar]], where the month may start from [[Lìchūn|Risshun]] to the day before [[Jingzhe|Keichitsu]].
