--> ==Years of Yang Fire Tiger== A year is classified as Heiin if its [[Gregorian calendar|Western calendar]] year, when divided by 60, leaves a remainder of 6. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Heiin Years''' |- ![[:en:1st millennium|1st millennium]]!![[:en:2nd millennium|2nd millennium]]!![[3rd millennium]] |- | *[[6]] *[[66]] *[[:en:126|126]] *[[:en:186|186]] *[[:en:246|246]] *[[:en:306|306]] *[[:en:366|366]] *[[426]] *[[486]] *[[546]] *[[606]] *[[666]] *[[726]] *[[786]] *[[846]] *[[906]] *[[966]] | *[[:en:1026|1026]] *[[:en:1086|1086]] *[[:en:1146|1146]] *[[:en:1206|1206]] *[[:en:1266|1266]] *[[:en:1326|1326]] *[[:en:1386|1386]] *[[:en:1446|1446]] *[[:en:1506|1506]] *[[:en:1566|1566]] *[[:en:1626|1626]] *[[:en:1686|1686]] *[[:en:1746|1746]] *[[:en:1806|1806]] *[[:en:1866|1866]] *[[:en:1926|1926]] *[[:en:1986|1986]] | *[[:en:2046|2046]] *[[:en:2106|2106]] *[[:en:2166|2166]] *[[:en:2226|2226]] *[[:en:2286|2286]] *[[:en:2346|2346]] *[[:en:2406|2406]] *[[:en:2466|2466]] *[[2526]] *[[2586]] *[[2646]] *[[:en:2706|2706]] *[[2766]] *[[2826]] *[[2886]] *[[:en:2946|2946]] |}
==Months of Yang Fire Tiger== The first month (January) of a year ending in 4 or 9 in the Western calendar (when the [[Heavenly Stems|stem]] is [[甲|Kō]] or [[己|Ki]]) is designated as a Heiin month. However, this is based on the [[Chinese lunar calendar|lunar calendar]] or the [[solar term calendar]], where the month may start from [[Lìchūn|Risshun]] to the day before [[Jingzhe|Keichitsu]].
==Days of Yang Fire Tiger== === Rekichū (Lower Section) === Heiin days in the [[Lower Section rekichū]] are as follows: * [[Unlucky Meeting Days]] (for the [[Chinese lunar calendar|lunar]] months of 3 and 9) == See Also == *{{prefix|qq=}} *{{intitle|qq=}}
